divs: Sighting DetailsSaw a bright luminesent orange redish light heading west over orcutt road when driving west on said road,appearing to slowly head out in the distance straight away but getting to the horizon the light then seemed to wobble or make small circles left and right,also at that time an airplane passed overhead slightly south and much higher than the object obviously an airplane.The light then decended or went west over the horizon.
